window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>His code name is Mr Clark. And his work for the CIA is brilliant, cold-blooded, and efficient...but who is he really? In a harrowing tour de force, Tom Clancy shows how an ordinary man named John Kelly crossed the lines of justice and morality - to become the CIA legend, Mr Clark. </p> <p>This is an unforgettable journey into the heart of darkness. Without mercy. Without guilt. Without remorse.</p>"; 
